Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.48,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.56,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.11,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.70,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.42,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:35.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.49,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.35,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.27,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:51.68,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:55.73,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.53,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:03.87,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.73,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:12.01,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.92,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.48,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:21.06,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:27.68,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.81,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:02.44,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.48,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.56,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所无法传达　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.52,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地里　在这样的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:16.11,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若梦　回眸几何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.70,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所制作的　玻璃饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.42,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一触　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:35.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.49,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至终　覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.35,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}爱　仅需一滴　脸颊便能浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.27,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀绞　雨恨云愁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:51.68,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还是对你　一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:55.73,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落泪　就此止泣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.53,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想与你　欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:03.87,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此向往　想象便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:07.73,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改变当下　于晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:12.01,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出发吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.92,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}携手与你共赏春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.48,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑云已散　风光日霁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:21.06,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨后镜花水月　依旧彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:27.68,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨过天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.81,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不过我想让你　所寻自己而已
